This directory contains NvRAM libnvram_platform interface, which defines the interface of
libnvram_platform and is used to build a libnvram_platform shared library.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
 It defines NvRAM platform info for this board(MT6582).

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================

It needs the following libs from AOSP:
1.  libc.so
2.  libcutils.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1.libnvram.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.


HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Files in this directory is used to
generate a shared library 'libnvram_platform.so'.

The shared library 'libnvram_platform.so' is called by
'libnvram.so','libfile_op.so' etc, which can handle NvRAM partiton layout or platform specific info.


All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
